[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "たくさんいて、キリがない……！\n果ての大陸まで、あとどれくらい！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00438",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "黄金星があそこで、あの星があそこだから……\nあと少しのはず！　もうちょっと、次さえ越えれば！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00439",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だが、次は……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00440",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "出たな、大物たち……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00441",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "前に撤退を余儀なくされた、\nあの大型魔物たちの群れ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00442",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "大丈夫か？　アルビーナの嬢ちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00443",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様なら、大丈夫。\n私たちだって、ついてる……ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00444",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。正直言うとめっちゃ怖い。\n見た瞬間、嫌な汗が全身から噴き出てきたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00445",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でも、もう逃げない。前回とは違う。\n身体も、技も、錬金術も鍛えてきたんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00446",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ここでまた逃げて、みんなを……\n自分自身を裏切るほうが怖い！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00447",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "なるほど……鍛えた成果が出たみたいだね。\n本人は知ってか知らずか、言わないでいるが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00448",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ええ、あの子が一番成長したのは、心です。\nとっても立派に、ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00449",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ふぅ……よし！　やってやる！\nアレ使うよ！　ベップ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00450",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "準備できてるわ、姉様！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_038_00451",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それってもしかしなくても、持ち物整理の時に\n陽動に使うって言ってたやつだね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_038_00452",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。アタシは案内人として、責任を持って\nみんなを目的地まで案内するんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00453",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "これを使って魔物を遠くに陽動し、その隙に\n煙幕に隠れながら進む……危険は少なくしたいものね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_038_00454",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "それでも船に張り付いてくる魔物はいるだろうから、\nそこは私たちの出番だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_164_038_00455",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。大変だけど、あとちょっとなんだ……\nみんな、行くよ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00456",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "絶対たどり着いてやる、果ての大陸……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_038_00457",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]